{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IT'S NEVER TOO LATE TO TURN YOUR LIFE AROUND!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/4__1_.png?t=1737055882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nerd Simulator is the game where you step into the shoes of a 40-year-old finally ready to leave the nest in this hilarious RPG-Life Simulation mix. Tackle wacky challenges, embrace absurd adventures, and prove that with determination (and a bit of chaos), you can start fresh at any age.\u00a0The fridge doesn\u2019t refill itself, and the clock is ticking. It\u2019s time to take control of your life, step out of her shadow, and prove that even at this age, you can turn it all around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/1__1_.png?t=1737055882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WTF IS THIS GAME?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Nerd Simulator</i> is a hilarious blend of dark humor, absurd challenges, and unpredictable twists. Your mission? Turn your life around one bizarre task at a time, from washing your socks without shrinking them to tackling epic milestones on the road to adulting (whatever that means).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/5.jpg?t=1737055882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ridiculous missions:</strong> Cook a meal that doesn\u2019t cause food poisoning, land a job that requires zero effort, and take on life\u2019s chaos with the finesse only a 40-year-old can muster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sharp, dark humor:</strong> Quirky dialogue, over-the-top characters, and endless moments that\u2019ll make you shout, \u201cWTF?!\u201d</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspiration through laughter:</strong> Even if your character is a complete disaster, this game reminds you it\u2019s never too late to rewrite your story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A lot of &quot;small things&quot;</strong>: 3D Interaction in the room, many mini-games, finding true love, a lot of unique puzzles...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/RoomActivities_GIF.gif?t=1737055882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can you conquer your laziness, win at life, and finally stop being\u2026 yourself?</strong> Or will your mom have to kick you out? The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buckle up, prepare for the wildest ride of your (mid)life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737055882","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/page.bg.jpg?t=1737055882","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/d5188cec5b32f1ac7d50941d7127907c0cdbc1f5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737055882","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/d5188cec5b32f1ac7d50941d7127907c0cdbc1f5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737055882","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":